mosinstall.name: rt_versatility_iii
mosinstall.author: rhuk
mosinstall.description:
RocketTheme Versatility III

Versatility III is a new slant on our most popular theme of all time, Versatility II. This time we've gone back to the drawing board and taken all of the best features of VII and incorporated all the latest and greatest features of the last few templates, plus added one brand new feature - RokMooMenu. It is not free or public. This is template is for members of the RocketTheme Joomla Template Club only. For installation help check out the 'Versatility III' Overview Page on the RocketTheme Template Club home page.
